## 13. Useful extensions

| Extension | What |
|---|---|
| `pg_stat_statements` | Query stats (must-have, # 1 troubleshooting tool) |
| `pgaudit` | Audit logging |
| `pgcrypto` | Cryptography functions (encrypt / hash) |
| `pg_trgm` | Trigram matching (fuzzy search, GIN-indexed LIKE patterns) |
| `pg_partman` | Partition management automation |
| `pg_repack` | Online table reorganization (vs `VACUUM FULL`) |
| `pg_uuidv7` | UUID v7 (built-in in PG 17+) |
| `PostGIS` | Geographic data |
| `TimescaleDB` | Time-series-optimized partitioning + compression |
| `vector` (pgvector) | Vector similarity search (AI/ML embeddings) |
| `hstore` | Key-value pairs (mostly superseded by JSONB) |

