## 15. External-specific checklist

В дополнение к `database-design-base.md` § 17:

- [ ] Latest stable PostgreSQL major version chosen
- [ ] Managed service выбран (или self-hosted с justified reason + DBA on team)
- [ ] TLS enforced (`sslmode=verify-full` clients)
- [ ] Encryption at rest enabled
- [ ] Backup configured (daily + WAL archive для PITR)
- [ ] PITR target RTO/RPO документированы (см. base.md § 14)
- [ ] Restore drill scheduled (quarterly minimum)
- [ ] `pg_stat_statements` extension installed
- [ ] Connection pooling sized; PgBouncer если total > max_connections
- [ ] Replication / HA setup (если product-tier requires)
- [ ] Indexes используют `CONCURRENTLY` (производственные)
- [ ] Multi-tenancy strategy выбрана (app-level + tenant_id default; RLS для hardening если applicable)
- [ ] UUID v7 для public-facing IDs
- [ ] `text` + CHECK constraints вместо native ENUM (миграции easier)
- [ ] JSONB только для truly schema-less data; GIN index если queried
- [ ] Partitioning только если § 2 base triggers met (table > 100M rows etc)
- [ ] Slow query log enabled (`log_min_duration_statement = 100ms` или project threshold)
- [ ] Autovacuum tuning per-table для high-churn tables
- [ ] Role hierarchy (app_reader / app_writer / app_migrator separated)
- [ ] `pg_hba.conf` ограничивает access (no `trust` auth, no `0.0.0.0/0` без SSL)
- [ ] Maintenance windows scheduled (major upgrades planned annually)
